videos.description: Arkansas strikes first with a 51-yard passing touchdown from Austin Allen to Dominique Reed to give the Razorbacks a 7-0 lead over Ole Miss.
videos.headline: Arkansas gets on board early with 51-yard TD

videos.description: Connor Limpert kickoff for 65 yds , Carlos Davis return for 39 yds to the Miss 39
videos.headline: Ole Miss 100-yard kick return Touchdown overturned

videos.description: Chad Kelly finds Evan Engram, who does the rest, powering his way for a 13-yard touchdown to put Ole Miss down one after the missed extra point against Arkansas.
videos.headline: Engram powers into the end zone for Ole Miss

videos.description: Austin Allen throws his second touchdown of the game on a 13-yard strike to Drew Morgan to increase Arkansas' lead to 14-6 over Ole Miss in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Allen fires second TD of the game

videos.description: Akeem Judd run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.headline: A. Judd run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Kelly keeps it for 8-yard TD

videos.headline: Arkansas loses 24 yards on a fumble

videos.description: After Arkansas DB Henre' Toliver makes a great one-handed interception, with DB De'Andre Coley getting called for a targeting penalty after he hits Ole Miss WR Van Jefferson in the helmet, resulting in an ejection.

videos.description: Arkansas QB Austin Allen tosses a shovel pass to RB Rawleigh Williams III, who then runs into the end zone for a touchdown as the Razorbacks take a 27-20 lead over Ole Miss.
